UDEMY REact w TS


-converting an existing react app into TS

npm install --save typescript @types/node @types/react @types/react-dom @types/jest


-now need to initialize a tsconfig

easy way to do this is by 

npx tsc --init

then in tsconfig

{
  "compilerOptions": {
    "jsx": "react"
  }
}


reference: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/50432556/cannot-use-jsx-unless-the-jsx-flag-is-provided


